Dangerous Love Sultry Nigerian songstress Tiwa Savage is back with a new single “Dangerous Love” and she announced the song via her Twitter page. “Dangerous Love” is the first official single off her forthcoming fourth studio album “Cella.” The Cracker Malio produced song is a blend of R$B and Afrobeats. The song plays around the subject of being in love with someone who is undeserving of the time and attention. The girl in question is well aware that her love interest is no good for her yet she gambles with her heart. This is one track every guy and lady can relate with”, Tiwa Savage says. “Dangerous Love” is a reminder that Tiwa Savage still has her game together and can deliver a powerful song anytime. Watch the lyrical video to “Dangerous Love” below:  